{"tid":1366803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"EO/AO圖聯署 公務員事務局急約晤入職十年內的AO","createTime":"2019-07-26T05:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T01:35:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":593,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"59e22f37451cee7cd81a99f189bb0cbd2d8b235c","tid":1366803,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:16:03.000Z","msg":"政府處理反修訂《逃犯條例》風波的手法引發公務員不滿，繼逾400名政府行政主任(EO)聯署表達憤怒及關注，有報道指政務主任(AO)職系正準備聯署，表達對當前局勢的擔憂，並要求成立獨立調查委員會調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，由現任及前政務主任發起的聯署主攻年輕政務主任，目標是最少100名政務主任。消息指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">公務員事務局副秘書長盧世雄昨日已約見部份入職約10年以內的政務主任，今日亦會再約其他年輕政務主任</span>。<br />\n<br />\n日前一名政務主任已在「連登」發文，並附上自己的職員證，批評特首林鄭月娥包庇黑社會，又指記者利君雅在記者會上要求林鄭月娥「講人話」大快人心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2201292/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2201292%2F&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=757136ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2201292/</a>"},{"pid":"57c1402f54af8e103506dad1322bf7d162a8bfdf","tid":1366803,"uid":59633,"like":154,"dislike":0,"score":154,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680c510417d1874a878ae8b5c513398ab15e8739","tid":1366803,"uid":212626,"like":374,"dislike":0,"score":374,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"正苦膠官開始做嘢<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n捉內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7239b84b18b4e00456497a49a15e4966c9511a6a","tid":1366803,"uid":191656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img s